long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en_GB,en_US,e:
**************** FEATURES ****************
💯70+ Best Prompt Templates 
Get your business done with 70+ best ChatGPT templates. We provide prompt ideas from blog outline, email newsletter to your favorite poem. You're free to cross your creative boundaries. 

🥰 Top Prompts
Explore our top ChatGPT prompts for SEO, Marketing, Art, Programming and more. Our users love them. You are only one click away. 

💰 Share Prompts
Share tried and tested prompts to others and receive donations when they like your prompts.

🙈 Code Syntax Highlighting
Responses include syntax highlighting for code, making it easier to read and understand technical information.

👨‍💻 Trigger Settings
Choose how to trigger, including always, manually, or with a question mark.

🤝 OpenAI Api Configs
The API that powers Web, free, but sometimes unstable.
OpenAI official API, more stable, charged by usage.

💁 Popup and Standalone Page
Available as a popup window within your browser or as a standalone page.

❓Ask Anything Anywhere
Ask ChatGPT anything, anytime, from anywhere within your browser.

👌 Right Click
Right click to send selected text to ChatGPT as a prompt

🌑 Dark Theme
The extension includes a dark theme for those who prefer a darker interface.

Install the extension and sit down for specific answers to your subjects!. The Extension will help you replace Merlin and AIPRM
